#: ../../metrics.rst:14
msgid ""
"You can install only one instance of Prometheus, usually on the leader "
"node. Prometheus does not require any configuration and it will be "
"exposed on a random URL. The URL is available at Prometheus instance "
"``Status`` page. You can access it from the software center or from the "
"application menu on the top-right corner."
msgstr ""

#: ../../metrics.rst:19
msgid ""
"You should install the node exporter on each cluster node. To install it,"
" access the :ref:`software_center-section` and look for the "
"``node_exporter`` application. Each time a new node with the exporter is "
"installed, Prometheus will automatic collect the node metrics."
msgstr ""

#: ../../metrics.rst:23
msgid ""
"Grafana can be installed only on the leader node. After install, you will"
" need to configure the ``Host name`` with a valid FQDN to access the "
"Grafana instance. Enable ``Let's Encrypt`` and ``HTTP to HTTPS`` options "
"accordingly to your needs."
msgstr ""

